<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Verify Your Account</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6">
    <h2>Welcome to Our Platform, <%- name %>!</h2>
    <p>
      Thank you for signing up. Please follow the rules of engagement on our
      platform to ensure a safe and enjoyable experience.
    </p>
    <p>Your One-Time Password (OTP) is:</p>
    <h3 style="color: #333; font-size: 24px"><%- otp %></h3>
    <p>
      This OTP is valid till <%- time %>. Please enter it in the verification
      form to complete your account setup.
    </p>
    <p>click on the button below to continue the verification process</p>
    <div style="width: 100%; display: flex; justify-content: center">
      <a
        style="
          padding: 5px 12px;
          border-radius: 5px;
          background-color: blue;
          color: white;
        "
        href="<%- url %>"
        >verify</a
      >
    </div>
    <p>We are excited to have you onboard!</p>
    <p>
      Best regards,<br />
      The Platform Team
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
